sabhyta - Ek baar ek car vala ek raste se gujar raha tha to achanak samne ek gadda aa gya jisme uski car ka pahiya fas gya. usne aas pass madad keliye dekha koi dikha nhi thodi der bad vaha ek vyakti aaya car ke malik ne kaha ki meri madad kardo car ko thoda sa dhakka marna he. us vyakti ne kaha thik he me madad kar dunga lekin me iske liye aapse 500 rupye lunga. car ke malik ne socha or kaha thik he. us vyakti ne car ko dhakka lagaya or car gadde se bahar aa gayi. car ke malik ne use 500 rs diye or vaha se aage bada.

sanskriti- Ab car vala thoda aage aaya or fir uske raste me ek or gadda aa gya usne koshish ki ki  gadde me pahiya na fase par gadde me pahiya fas gya. ab pas me hi ek vyakti dikha. vah vyakti car ke pass aaya. ab car ke malik ke  man aaya ki vapas 500 ka chuna laga gya. ab car ke malik ne us vyakti ko madad ke liye bola or vah vyakti ne uski car ko dhakka lagaya or car ka pahiya gadde me se bahar nikal gya. car ke malik ne pese ka kaha par vyakti ne mana kar diya or kaha iski koi jarurat nhi he or yah bhi kaha ki aage 2 gadde or aayenge dhayan se jana.

vikruti - To ek ladka ek kapde ki dukkan par jata he. or paint dekhne lagta he 12000 ki usne paint dekhi jo ki fasion vali thi kai jagah se fati hui. usne dukandar ko kaha ki thodi or jyada fati vali paint batao. to yah ho hoti he vikruti
